These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: r&b, gospel, folk, funk, soul, metal, electronic
1. the fan of metal is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
2. the fan of r&b is on the left of the fan of funk##1
3. the fan of electronic is on the left of the fan of folk##1
4. the fan of soul is between the fan of r&b and the fan of folk##2
5. the fan of funk is between the fan of gospel and the fan of r&b##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3   |    4    |  5  |   6   |   7   |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | folk | soul | r&b | funk | gospel | metal |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-2::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: woodworking, drawing, cooking, sudoku, puzzles, board-games, dancing
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
4. the person who's hobby is cooking is between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2
5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
6. the person who's hobby is cooking is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |   3    |   4   |     5      |    6    |     7      |
| Hobby   | board-games | dancing | woodworking | cooking | sudoku | drawing | puzzles |

 #################################

 
